2015年4月2日，在瑞士洛桑舉行的伊朗核问题部长级談判中，伊朗與伊核问题六国（P5+1）經過八天的馬拉松式談判後達成框架協議，伊朗同意將用作提煉[[濃縮鈾|濃縮鈾]]的離心機數目由現時一萬九千台削減至約六千台；未來十五年，停止提煉濃度百分之三以上的濃縮鈾，以及停止建造新提煉設施，現有的提煉設施大部分關閉或改建為研究和訓練中心，伊朗又同意給國際原子能機構的人員進入所有核設施，监督協議落實情況。當所有承諾落實後，歐盟和美國將會撤銷對伊朗的經濟制裁，聯合國亦會解除所有針對伊朗核計劃的決議案<ref>{{cite news | title = 伊朗核談達成『框架』協議 | publisher = [[BBC|BBC中文網]] | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/04/150402_iran_talks_breakthrough | author = 歐陽成 | date = 2015-04-02 | accessdate = 2015-04-02 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2015-04-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150406094657/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/04/150402_iran_talks_breakthrough | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>Jethro Mullen & Nic Robertson, [http://www.cnn.com/2015/07/14/politics/iran-nuclear-deal/ "Landmark deal reached on Iran nuclear program"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/07/14/politics/iran-nuclear-deal/ |date=20150714100219 }}, CNN (14 July 2015).</ref><ref name="Gordon">Michael R. Gordon & David E. Sanger, [https://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/15/world/middleeast/iran-nuclear-deal-is-reached-after-long-negotiations.html "Deal Reached on Iran Nuclear Program; Limits on Fuel Would Lessen With Time"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/15/world/middleeast/iran-nuclear-deal-is-reached-after-long-negotiations.html |date=20170120105536 }}, ''The New York Times'' (14 July 2015).</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = 伊朗與六國在核問題達成框架協議 | publisher = 商業電台 | url = https://hk.news.yahoo.com/伊朗與六國在核問題達成框架協議-182800627.html | date = 2015-04-03 | accessdate = 2015-04-06 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2020-08-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200820062345/https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E8%88%87%E5%85%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%A8%E6%A0%B8%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E9%81%94%E6%88%90%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-182800627.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。各方將繼續磋商細節，尋求在2015年6月30日前達成最終協議。協議有效期是十五年，尤其是開首十年，伊朗製造核武的能力將受到重大限制。這使得即使伊朗違反協議，也需要一年才可製造出一枚核彈，使國際社會有充裕時間應對<ref>{{cite news | title = 伊朗與六國達成核問題框架協議 | publisher = 有線新聞 | url = http://cablenews.i-cable.com/webapps/news_video/index.php?news_id=455291 | date = 2015-04-03 | accessdate = 2015-04-06 | language = zh-hant}}</ref>。

2015年5月，美国国会以大比数通过《{{tsl|en|Iran Nuclear Agreement Review Act of 2015|2015年伊朗核协议審查法}}》，该法授权美国国会审查联邦政府与伊朗签订的核协议<ref name="报道0714A">{{cite news|title=U.S. House passes Iran nuclear review legislation|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2015/05/14/us-iran-nuclear-usa-idUSKBN0NZ29M20150514|agency=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=May 14, 2015|author=Patricia Zengerle|accessdate=2019-07-14|archive-date=2015-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151114215953/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/05/14/us-iran-nuclear-usa-idUSKBN0NZ29M20150514|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。并规定《聯合全面行動計畫》对美国而言是一項不具約束力的政治承諾，在美国法律中不具有行政协议的效力<ref>{{cite web |url=http://opiniojuris.org/2015/03/11/dealing-with-iran-a-primer-on-the-presidents-options-for-a-nuclear-agreement/ |title=Dealing with Iran: A Primer on the President's Options for a Nuclear Agreement |accessdate=9 December 2015 |archive-date=2020-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208020823/http://opiniojuris.org/2015/03/11/dealing-with-iran-a-primer-on-the-presidents-options-for-a-nuclear-agreement/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://2009-2017.state.gov/documents/organization/65728.pdf |title=International documents of a non-legally binding character |publisher=U.S. State Department |accessdate=9 December 2015 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029064500/https://2009-2017.state.gov/documents/organization/65728.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="PhillipsExec">Amber Phillips, [https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2015/07/09/the-role-of-congress-or-lack-thereof-in-the-iran-deal-explained/ "Can Congress stop the Iran deal?"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-fix/wp/2015/07/09/the-role-of-congress-or-lack-thereof-in-the-iran-deal-explained/ |date=20201117060714 }}, ''The Washington Post'' (1 July 2015).</ref><ref name="BomboyExec">Scott Bomboy, [http://blog.constitutioncenter.org/2015/07/veto-showdown-on-tap-for-congress-after-iran-nuclear-deal/ "Veto showdown on tap for Congress after Iran nuclear deal"] {{Wayback|url=http://blog.constitutioncenter.org/2015/07/veto-showdown-on-tap-for-congress-after-iran-nuclear-deal/ |date=20150724161256 }}, National Constitution Center (15 July 2015).</ref>。美国白宫当时则批评该法案使伊核协议谈判复杂化，并曾威胁否决该法案<ref name="cn20150320">{{cite web |author1=中新网 |title=美国会4月将表决伊核协议审查法案 静待谈判成果 |url=http://www.chinanews.com/m/gj/2015/03-20/7145005.shtml |website=中国新闻网 |accessdate=2019-07-14 |location=北京 |language=zh-cn |archive-date=2020-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820061310/http://www.chinanews.com/m/gj/2015/03-20/7145005.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年7月14日，會談各方宣佈達成伊朗核问题全面协议——《联合全面行动计划》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://eeas.europa.eu/statements/docs/2013/131124_03_en.pdf|title=Joint Plan of Action|publisher=[[European_External_Action_Service|European External Action Service]]|date=24 November 2013|ref={{sfnref|Joint Plan of Action}}|accessdate=18 October 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131125154022/http://eeas.europa.eu/statements/docs/2013/131124_03_en.pdf|archive-date=2013-11-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 落实阶段 ===
{{参见|聯合國安全理事會第2231號決議}}
根據《聯合全面行動計畫》的規定，必須取得聯合國安理會的正式認可，协议方可产生[[国际法|国际法]]效力<ref name="Thomson">[http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/iran-nuclear-deal-un-security-council-likely-to-vote-next-week-1.3152376 "Iran nuclear deal: UN Security Council likely to vote next week: US diplomats to promote deal to UN counterparts in coming days"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/iran-nuclear-deal-un-security-council-likely-to-vote-next-week-1.3152376 |date=20200923162835 }}, CBC, Thomson Reuters (15 July 2015).</ref><ref name="Sengupta">Somini Sengupta, [https://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/16/world/consensus-gives-security-council-momentum-in-mideast-but-question-is-how-much.html Consensus Gives Security Council Momentum in Mideast, but Question Is How Much] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/16/world/consensus-gives-security-council-momentum-in-mideast-but-question-is-how-much.html |date=20210110161250 }}, ''The New York Times'' (16 July 2015).</ref><ref name="UNSCScheduled">CBS News/Associated Press, [http://www.cbsnews.com/news/un-security-council-vote-iran-nuclear-deal-resolution-us-congress-objections/ Iran deal set to become international law] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/un-security-council-vote-iran-nuclear-deal-resolution-us-congress-objections/ |date=20210213213042 }} (17 July 2015).</ref><ref name="UNSCRes">Somini Sengupta, [https://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/21/world/middleeast/security-council-following-iran-nuclear-pact-votes-to-lift-sanctions.html "U.N. Moves to Lift Sanctions on Iran After Nuclear Deal"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/21/world/middleeast/security-council-following-iran-nuclear-pact-votes-to-lift-sanctions.html |date=20210123215903 }}, ''The New York Times'' (20 July 2015).</ref>。2015年7月20日，联合国安理会通过[[聯合國安全理事會第2231號決議|聯合國安全理事會第2231號決議]]，以敦促执行《联合全面行动计划》的时间表，并对解除对伊朗的制裁做出了一些措施。<ref>[http://www.un.org/press/en/2015/sc11974.doc.htm Security Council, Adopting Resolution 2231 (2015), Endorses Joint Comprehensive Agreement on Iran’s Nuclear Programme] {{Wayback|url=http://www.un.org/press/en/2015/sc11974.doc.htm |date=20210110082450 }} ''United Nations''</ref>

2016年1月17日，[[国际原子能机构|国际原子能机构]]总干事天野之弥证实伊朗完成了开始执行伊核全面协议的必要准备步骤。美国白宫同日发表声明说，总统奥巴马已签署行政命令，根据伊核协议规定取消对伊朗的经济制裁。莫盖里尼和扎里夫同日宣布，鉴于伊朗履行了伊核问题全面协议承诺，与伊朗核问题有关的经济和金融制裁按照全面协议要求当天得到解除<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guancha.cn/economy/2016_01_17_348336.shtml |title=伊朗完成伊核协议执行准备 美欧解除经济制裁 |accessdate=2016-10-23 |archive-date=2016-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611063937/http://www.guancha.cn/economy/2016_01_17_348336.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。美國於2017年4月和2017年7月確認伊朗遵守該協議<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/apr/19/iran-nuclear-deal-trump-administration-approves-agreement-but-review-looms|title=Iran nuclear deal: Trump administration approves agreement but review looms|date=19 April 2017|work=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|accessdate=14 May 2019|archive-date=2019-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514074046/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/apr/19/iran-nuclear-deal-trump-administration-approves-agreement-but-review-looms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Baker |first=Peter |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/07/17/us/politics/trump-iran-nuclear-deal-recertify.html |title=Trump Recertifies Iran Nuclear Deal, but Only Reluctantly |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=17 July 2017 |accessdate=14 May 2019 |archive-date=2019-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514075129/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/07/17/us/politics/trump-iran-nuclear-deal-recertify.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

