== 評論 ==
{{参见|{{tsl|en|Views on the nuclear program of Iran|对伊朗核計劃的评论}}}}
全球共有90多個國家对伊核问题全面协议表示认可与赞赏<ref>Jacob J. Lew, [http://www.nytimes.com/2015/08/14/opinion/the-high-price-of-rejecting-the-iran-deal.html The High Price of Rejecting the Iran Deal] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/08/14/opinion/the-high-price-of-rejecting-the-iran-deal.html |date=20150817000655 }}, ''New York Times'' (August 13, 2015).</ref>。美國總統[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]表示，其已达成美国與伊朗的“歷史性和解”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-32166814|title=Iran nuclear talks: 'Framework' deal agreed|date=2 April 2015|publisher=[[BBC_Online|BBC Online]]|accessdate=2 April 2015|archive-date=2018-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619185620/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-32166814|dead-url=no}}</ref>。奧巴馬還表示，此次谈判达成了美国的核心目标，伊核问题全面协议是一个良好的协议<ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/04/02/world/iran-nuclear-talks/|title=Iran nuclear deal framework announced - CNN.com|author=Elise Labott, Mariano Castillo and Catherine E. Shoichet, CNN|date=2 April 2015|work=CNN|accessdate=2019-07-13|archive-date=2017-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170501073531/http://edition.cnn.com/2015/04/02/world/iran-nuclear-talks|dead-url=no}}</ref>。中国外交部長[[王毅|王毅]]指出，全面协议最重要的成果就是维护了国际核不扩散体系，伊朗方面作出了不发展核武器的政治承诺，各方以有约束力的国际协议方式将这一承诺固定下来。同时给予伊方和平利用核能的正当权力，伊与各方的关系也翻开了新的一页<ref>{{cite news | title = 王毅：中国为达成伊核全面协议发挥了独特的建设性作用 | publisher = 中华人民共和国外交部 | url = http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/wjbz_673089/zyhd_673091/t1281346.shtml | date = 2015-07-14 | author =  | accessdate = 2016-01-18 | language = zh-Hans | archive-date = 2019-06-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190616210332/https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/wjbz_673089/zyhd_673091/t1281346.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[欧盟外交和安全政策高级代表|欧盟外交和安全政策高级代表]][[费代丽卡·莫盖里尼|费代丽卡·莫盖里尼]]和伊朗外交部長查瑞夫（Javad Zarif）發表聯合聲明，肯定核子談判協議的達成，「這是歷史性的一天」<ref>{{cite news | title = 達成伊朗核協議 歐盟暫停制裁延6個月 | publisher = 中央社 | url = http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201507150009-1.aspx | date = 2015-07-15 | author = 江今葉 | accessdate = 2016-01-18 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2017-03-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170307104135/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201507150009-1.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref>。伊朗總統[[哈桑·鲁哈尼|哈桑·鲁哈尼]]說：“伊朗是守諾言的國家，於維護國家利益前題下，任何在核問題談判許下的承諾，伊朗都會遵守<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.presstv.ir/Detail/2015/04/03/404516/Iran-to-fulfill-promises-if-P51-does|title=Iran to abide by its promises if P5+1 group fulfills its obligations: Rouhani|author=|date=3 April 2015|accessdate=3 April 2015|work=Press TV|archive-date=2015-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150405205730/http://www.presstv.ir/Detail/2015/04/03/404516/Iran-to-fulfill-promises-if-P51-does|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[欧洲理事会主席|欧洲理事会主席]][[唐納德·圖斯克|唐納德·圖斯克]]表示，伊核問題新協議打破了長達13年的伊朗核問題僵局，如果下一步措施完全得以落實，將為歐盟與伊朗合作鋪平道路<ref>{{cite news | title = 歐盟表示對伊朗制裁凍結期限延長至明年1月 | publisher = 國際日報 | url = http://www.chinesetoday.com/big/article/1020590 | date = 2015-07-15 | author = 孫奕 | accessdate = 2016-01-18 | language = zh-hant | archive-date = 2020-08-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200820061902/http://www.chinesetoday.com/big/article/1020590 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。梵蒂岡發出一份聲明：「關於伊朗核計劃的協議，[[聖座|聖座]]以積極的眼光看待 。」<ref>Antonia Blumberg, [http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/vatican-iran-nuclear-deal_55a55160e4b0a47ac15d8f6d Vatican Says It Views Iran Deal In a 'Positive Light'] {{Wayback|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/vatican-iran-nuclear-deal_55a55160e4b0a47ac15d8f6d |date=20150715182303 }}, ''The Huffington Post'' (July 14, 2015).</ref>

以色列总统[[鲁文·里夫林|鲁文·里夫林]]表示以色列不接受框架協議，並稱伊核问题全面协议威胁以色列的国家安全<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/04/03/us-israel-iran-framework-idUSKBN0MU0BR20150403|title=Netanyahu tells Obama Iran deal threatens Israel; to convene top ministers|work=Reuters|accessdate=2019-07-13|archive-date=2015-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929173946/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/04/03/us-israel-iran-framework-idUSKBN0MU0BR20150403|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2015/04/03/netanyahu-on-collision-course-with-allies-in-wake-iran-deal-framework/|title=Netanyahu to Obama: Iran deal would 'threaten the survival of Israel'|work=Fox News|access-date=2016-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151023072134/http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2015/04/03/netanyahu-on-collision-course-with-allies-in-wake-iran-deal-framework/|archive-date=2015-10-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4644036,00.html|title=PM: Iran must commit to recognizing Israel's right to exist in final deal|work=ynet|access-date=2019-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409015818/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4644036,00.html|archive-date=2015-04-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

